 Highly-rated crooner, Innocent Idibia, better known as Tuface has built and commissioned a music studio in Obafemi Awolowo University. The veteran music star revealed that he was once honoured by the school by being inducted into the school of music as a Fellow. He therefore made his presence felt by erecting a music studio in the school. He further disclosed that Benue State University would be next. Sharing some videos on Instagram, he wrote: “Sometime ago i was honoured by the Great OAU as i was inducted into the school of music as A Fellow Of The School of music. today i just commissioned the multimillion # studio i built for the music department in OAU ile-ife.
upnext is Benue State University
